{"word":"ἀνόητος","slug":"ἀνόητος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀνόητος, ον</el></b> [<el>ἀ-</el><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ priv.\">priv.</a>, <el>νοητός</el> ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pert. to\">pert. to</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νοῦς\">νοῦς</a></el>, mental’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νοέω\">νοέω</a></el>; ‘not thought on, not understood’] ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pert. to\">pert. to</a> being without sense’, of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><i>mindless, dense, unintelligent</i> <a href='B:490 24:25'>Lk 24:25</a>; <a href='B:520 1:14'>Ro 1:14</a>; <a href='B:550 3:1'>Gal 3:1</a>, <a href='B:550 3:3'>3</a>; <a href='B:630 3:3'>Tit 3:3</a>;</b> of desires <b><i>making no sense</i> <a href='B:610 6:9'>1 Tim 6:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἅννας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄνοια\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}